#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:287
msgid ""
"Files can be duplicated, converted to a different format, converted to "
"TLV (Smart Raster image) format, renamed, premultiplied, and you can "
"choose to separate their colors."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:289
msgid ""
"When duplicating files, the new files will be renamed by appending an "
