#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:978
msgid ""
"Use the **Paste** command to paste the selection kept in memory into the "
"Xsheet/Timeline, starting from the selected insertion cell. The command "
"causes the following cells in the Xsheet to shift down, or in the "
"Timeline, to shift to the right."
